educationAims: '<div class="PSLONGEDITBOX" id="UN_PAM_CRSE_DTL_UN_AIMS$0" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><br><p>An important feature of the MSc programme in Entrepreneurship is the wide application of experiential learning. The students learn a broad knowledge of business practice and develop a range of skills in the core modules at the start of the course. The business plan is an opportunity for the students to draw all these aspects together.</p></div>',
